<div class="container my-4">
    <div class="card" style="max-width: 90%;">
        <div class="card-header text-center">
            <h2 class="display-6">The Monastery of Batalha</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <img src="~/Imagens/Adventures/Monastery/Monastery1.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Monastery">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <div class="mt-2">
                        <div class=" display-6 text-center">
                            <h5>A morning at the Monastery</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
                                <p>
                                    Hello, I'm Samanta Bordallo, a 26-year-old with a passion for inquiry and learning. Originally graduating in Biological Sciences in Brazil, I furthered my studies with a postgraduate degree in Criminal Expertise & Forensic Sciences. In September 2022, I embarked on a new adventure, moving to Portugal with my husband, marking a new chapter in my personal and professional journey.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    My foray into the programming world began in July 2019, during an interrupted master's program in Belém do Pará, where I had the chance to familiarize myself with the R language and R Studio, applying them in data-driven projects. This experience sowed the seeds of my growing interest in technology.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    In December 2022, my path led me deeper into this universe when I began self-taught studies in Python, supplemented by a course on UDEMY. I delved deeper by starting a .NET programming course through IEFP, developing projects in C# and C++, and recently diving into development with ASP.NET Core.
                                </p>
                            </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 15px;"></div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
